text: Marta Pustišek (21 February 1917 - 2 August 1966) was a Slovenian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
